import styles from "./css/Dropdown.module.css"

function Dropdown(){
    return(
        <>
            <label for="cars" className={styles.drop-down}>Select a Car</label>
            <select name="cars">
                <option>Audi</option>
                <option>Benz</option>
                <option>BMW</option>
                <option>Volvo</option>
            </select>
        </>
        
    )
}

export default Dropdown
